data.description: Beautiful 4 bedrooms home with a spacious, open, floor plan and plenty of natural lighting.  Ceiling Fans throughout and Water Softener. New roof April 2023. Extended Trex deck in the back off the covered patio.  Only one side neighbor, larger lot.  The backyard is nice and shaded in the afternoon with mature trees.
